high_descs: Walk forward and veer left to the microwave.
Pick up the egg on the right in the microwave.
Turn left and walk to the fridge.
Place the egg in the fridge to the right of the pot. Close the door, wait a moment, and then take the egg out again.
Take a step right and face the microwave.
Place the egg back in the microwave in front of and to the right of the other egg.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled egg in the microwave.

high_descs: Move forward, face the microwave on the left.
Take the egg on the right out of the microwave.
Turn left, bring the egg to the fridge, turn right to face the fridge.
Chill the egg in the fridge.
Bring the chilled egg back to the microwave on the right.
Put the egg in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled egg in the microwave.

high_descs: Remove an egg from the microwave.
Turn to your left and approach the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the egg inside, wait a little while, and remove the egg.
Turn to your right and approach the microwave.
Place the egg in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooled egg in the microwave.
